The Kitui government has hired 2,156 nursery school teachers under an annual budget of Sh260 million. A report from Kitui Governor Julius Malombe s office on efforts made to modernise ECDE says the county has also built classrooms. Modern classrooms are fast replacing grass-thatch mud houses or trees for classrooms. We ve build 501 new ECDE classrooms across the county and rehabilitated five others, it says.